{"type": "article", "id": 57486, "title": "Prada 广告大片《送货人》好看，Adobe 发布了一些黑科技 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2018-10-19T01:53:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 64, "name": "广告"}, {"id": 144, "name": "Adobe"}, {"id": 779, "name": "Prada"}, {"id": 68, "name": "苹果"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 103970, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 99, "image": "img/article/article_show/201810190920045O3cs2RqTZmKPpgF.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">又是跨界</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/rimowa-and-aesop-join-forces-1202887430/\" rel=\"nofollow\">德国行李箱制造商&nbsp;Rimowa&nbsp;和澳大利亚美容品牌 Aesop 合作了一个限量版项目</a></strong>：铝制旅行套装。Rimowa 提供包装，Aesop 提供里面的洗发水啥的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181019085136875aqWC1vdlrhpm3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.648438\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>值得一提的 Case</h3><p>苹果将于 10 月 30 日召开大会，预计推出无边框的新款 iPad Pro 和一些更新的 MacBook。为了大会的电子邀请函，<a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/tldr/2018/10/18/17995368/apple-october-30th-event-custom-logo-roundup\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>苹果设计了超过 30 种苹果标识的演绎</strong></a>：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201810190848188qbIcjx2S4QFrXOv.png\" data-ratio=\"0.562411\" data-format=\"webp\"><figcaption><p>图片来自 the verge</p></figcaption> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181019085012nc7yZjtXzgJSqKuE.png\" data-ratio=\"0.609547\" data-format=\"WEBP\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181019085011sjJEGRfxQi14c3aU.png\" data-ratio=\"0.551163\" data-format=\"WEBP\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181019085010JSwGFUx1HzkNPtnW.png\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"webp\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181019085011h83JbHBNZsimVkSC.png\" data-ratio=\"0.585629\" data-format=\"WEBP\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201810190850103SBfCXnZM7Dvu6gp.png\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"webp\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018101908501083v9nYLhV4qHuyoP.png\" data-ratio=\"0.622386\" data-format=\"WEBP\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181019085011GjA0MQEi2kgtCN83.png\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"webp\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181019085011K9IjMyidp83HskwX.png\" data-ratio=\"0.633750\" data-format=\"WEBP\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181019085011M04EmL1WfkI6HyK5.png\" data-ratio=\"0.644357\" data-format=\"WEBP\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2018/10/18/reading-let-us-stick-to-the-whole-self/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kindle 新款 Paperwhite 发布广告《我是阅读继承者》。</a></strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=j0753uxndcj\"></iframe> </figure> </div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201810190911096mjQSPJBrkRudbYA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.738095\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181019091126GNKnWRp8So51daZJ.png\" data-ratio=\"0.296825\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/749mCT8HX57YJZT1Ug8v1Q\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Prada《送货员》系列三部曲上线</strong></a>，由著名制片人 Ryan Hope 创作及执导，致敬经典 Cahier 手袋。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=h0751u4upo5\"></iframe><figcaption>午夜快递</figcaption> <div><div><div>&nbsp;</div></div></div></figure> </div><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=q07515oqfd1\"></iframe><figcaption>她的密友</figcaption> <div><div><div>&nbsp;</div></div></div></figure> </div><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=e0751a9xblx\"></iframe><figcaption>爱之优先权</figcaption> <div><div><div>&nbsp;</div></div></div></figure> </div><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/?p=1202886749&amp;preview=true&amp;preview_id=1202886749\" rel=\"nofollow\">Adidas Originals 正在尝试新的广告发布方式</a></strong>。品牌最新和潮流媒体 Complex 合作，后者邀请 Colin Tilley 执导了一段广告片，内容是关于 Curtis Roach，一位来自底特律的 19 岁说唱歌手，广告将在 Instagram Stories 中亮相，且仅存在 24 小时。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181019085431ngV9h3WFmp1OX6ro.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.648438\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.digitalartsonline.co.uk/news/creative-software/adobes-groundbreaking-prototypes-of-new-features-apps-for-creative-cloud/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Adobe 发布了一些可能改变设计流程的黑科技</strong></a>。昨天的 Adobe Max Sneak Peaks 上，Adobe 展示了一些正在开发中的技术。动画笔刷 Brush Bounty，可以简单在画面中用笔刷刷出动画效果；</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181019090412RqiAOT3czDIegJdw.png\" data-ratio=\"0.532813\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p>所见即所得的包装设计 Fantastic Fold 可以帮设计师省去构思 3D 包装上图案平面图的烦恼；</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181019090528ht0q2J7wrEWk3mMi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.561333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>Fast Mask 是一种功能更强大的蒙版；Fontphoria 则可以通过机器识别“复制”字体的样式 。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181019090544WrYv6AP53e8wgLZU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.653333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201810190906052UJ8QHFnXvoZyeA0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.561333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>题图来自 Prada</p>"}